{{Infobox language |name=Alladian |states=[[Ivory Coast]] |speakers=23,000 |date=1993 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Niger-Congo |fam2=[[Atlantic–Congo]] |fam3=[[Kwa languages|Kwa]] |fam4=Avikam–Alladian |iso3=ald |glotto=alla1248 |glottorefname=Alladian }}
'''Alladian''' (Alladyan, Allagia, Allagian) is one of the [[Lagoon languages]] of [[Ivory Coast]]. It is a [[Kwa languages|Kwa language]], closely related to [[Avikam language|Avikam]], but otherwise its position is unclear.
